---
layout: base.njk
title: "big. — Coaching and facilitation for leaders"
titleRaw: "big."
description: "Big. is the coaching practice of Al Reid — thirty years in the creative industry, now working with founders, MDs and leaders who want to do it well."
---

{% block head %}
<style>
  .inner { padding: var(--section-v) var(--pad); }
  .grid-half { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:var(--col-gap); align-items:start; }
  .grid-two-thirds { display:grid; grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr; gap:var(--col-gap); align-items:start; }
  .deco-rule { display:block; width:56px; height:1px; background:var(--red); border:none; margin:36px 0 0; }

  .hero { border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--rule); }
  .hero .inner { padding-top:104px; padding-bottom:100px; }
  .hero-provocation { font-size:58px; font-weight:400; line-height:1.1; letter-spacing:-0.035em; margin-bottom:24px; max-width:760px; }
  .hero-strapline { font-size:32px; font-weight:400; line-height:1.25; letter-spacing:-0.02em; color:var(--ink-muted); max-width:760px; }
  .hero-strapline .paren { color:var(--red); font-style:italic; }
  .hero-strapline .bigger { display:inline-block; font-size:1.18em; letter-spacing:-0.04em; color:var(--ink); opacity:0; transform:scale(0.88); transform-origin:left center; animation:grow 1s cubic-bezier(0.25,0.46,0.45,0.94) 0.4s forwards; }
  @keyframes grow { to { opacity:1; transform:scale(1); } }

  .who { border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--rule); background:var(--cream-mid); }
  .who-headline { font-size:64px; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:-0.04em; line-height:1.0; }
  .who-body { font-family:'Lato',sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:300; color:var(--ink-mid); line-height:1.85; padding-top:6px; }

  .services { border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--rule); }
  .services-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:0; border-top:0.5px solid var(--rule); margin-top:8px; }
  .service-item { padding:32px var(--col-gap) 32px 0; border-right:0.5px solid var(--rule); }
  .service-item:last-child { border-right:none; padding-right:0; padding-left:var(--col-gap); }
  .service-name { font-size:22px; font-weight:400; letter-spacing:-0.02em; line-height:1.2; margin-bottom:8px; }
  .service-desc { font-family:'Lato',sans-serif; font-size:14px; color:var(--ink-muted); line-height:1.65; }
  .service-link { display:inline-block; margin-top:14px; font-family:'Lato',sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:var(--red); text-decoration:none; }

  .testimony { border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--rule); background:var(--cream-mid); }
  .testimony-quote { font-size:26px; font-weight:400; line-height:1.55; letter-spacing:-0.015em; max-width:780px; }
  .testimony-quote::before { content:'\201C'; color:var(--red); }
  .testimony-quote::after  { content:'\201D'; color:var(--red); }
  .testimony-attr { margin-top:28px; font-family:'Lato',sans-serif; font-size:13px; color:var(--ink-faint); }
  .testimony-attr strong { font-weight:500; color:var(--ink-mid); margin-right:8px; }

  .about { border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--rule); }
  .about-body { font-family:'Lato',sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:300; color:var(--ink-mid); line-height:1.85; }
  .about-body p+p { margin-top:16px; }
  .about-link { display:inline-block; margin-top:24px; font-family:'Lato',sans-serif; font-size:13px; color:var(--red); text-decoration:none; }
  .about-img { aspect-ratio:4/3; }
  .about-img img { object-position:center 40%; }

  .thinking-section { border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--rule); background:var(--cream-mid); }
  .thinking-header { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; padding:24px var(--pad); border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--rule); }
  .thinking-header .label { margin-bottom:0; }
  .thinking-header a { font-family:'Lato',sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:var(--red); text-decoration:none; }
  .thinking-posts { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr); max-width:var(--max-w); margin:0 auto; }
  .post { padding:36px 40px; border-right:0.5px solid var(--rule); }
  .post:last-child { border-right:none; }
  .post-tag { font-family:'Lato',sans-serif; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; color:var(--red); margin-bottom:12px; }
  .post-title { font-size:16px; font-weight:400; line-height:1.42; margin-bottom:14px; letter-spacing:-0.01em; }
  .post-title a { color:var(--ink); text-decoration:none; }
  .post-title a:hover { color:var(--red); }
  .post-date { font-family:'Lato',sans-serif; font-size:11px; color:var(--ink-faint); }

  .site-footer { padding:28px var(--pad); display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; border-top:0.5px solid var(--rule); }
  .footer-logo { font-size:16px; font-weight:400; color:var(--ink-mid); text-decoration:none; }
  .footer-logo .stop { color:var(--red); }
  .footer-links { display:flex; gap:28px; list-style:none; }
  .footer-links a { font-family:'Lato',sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:var(--ink-faint); text-decoration:none; }
  .footer-contact a { font-family:'Lato',sans-serif; font-size:12px; color:var(--red); text-decoration:none; }

  @media (max-width:768px) {
    .grid-half,.grid-two-thirds,.services-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .hero .inner { padding-top:64px; padding-bottom:64px; }
    .hero-provocation { font-size:36px; }
    .hero-strapline { font-size:22px; }
    .who-headline { font-size:48px; }
    .service-item { border-right:none; border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--rule); padding:28px 0; }
    .service-item:last-child { padding-left:0; border-bottom:none; }
    .about-img { aspect-ratio:3/2 !important; }
    .thinking-posts { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    .post { border-right:none; border-bottom:0.5px solid var(--rule); padding:28px var(--pad); }
    .post:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
    .site-footer { flex-direction:column; gap:20px; text-align:center; }
  }
</style>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="hero-provocation">You know something needs to change.</div>
      <div class="hero-strapline">I help make your ideas a little<br><span class="paren">(or a lot)</span> <span class="bigger">bigger.</span></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="who">
    <div class="inner">
      <span class="label">Who it's for</span>
      <div class="grid-half">
        <div class="who-headline">Smart.<br>Nice.<br>Good.</div>
        <div class="who-body">People who are good at what they do — but want to do more of it, or something different. Who are a little stuck, a little lost, or just want to move faster. People who want some help, some support, and some challenge. Who want to work out what actually matters and how to get there. Open to learning, and ready to grow — their effectiveness, their idea, their company, their people.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="services">
    <div class="inner">
      <span class="label">What I do</span>
      <div class="services-grid">
        <div class="service-item">
          <div class="service-name">Coaching</div>
          <div class="service-desc">Getting you closer to where you want to be.</div>
          <a href="/work/" class="service-link">How it works →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="service-item">
          <div class="service-name">Facilitation</div>
          <div class="service-desc">Getting your team closer to where it wants to be.</div>
          <a href="/work/" class="service-link">How it works →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="testimony">
    <div class="inner">
      <span class="label">What they say</span>
      <div class="testimony-quote">Al has helped me join the dots. It's rare that someone gets purpose and culture to the same degree as commercial and brand. That's why I chose to work with Al.</div>
      <hr class="deco-rule">
      <div class="testimony-attr"><strong>Anthony Prior</strong> Organisational Strategist, Creative Industries</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="about">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="grid-half">
        <div>
          <span class="label">Who I am</span>
          <div class="about-body">
            <p>I'm Alastair Reid — most people call me Al. Thirty years making and shaping things. The last twelve, mostly people.</p>
            <p>I'm a better listener than I am anything else. I work from coffee shops, Zoom calls, and when the problem is knotty enough, a farm in Sussex with a fire going. I have 4,400 records and counting.</p>
          </div>
          <hr class="deco-rule">
          <a href="/about/" class="about-link">More about me →</a>
        </div>
        <div class="about-img img-wrap"><img src="/images/IMG_6789.jpg" alt="Moka pot brewing on an open fire in a Sussex field"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="thinking-section">
    <div class="thinking-header">
      <span class="label">Thinking</span>
      <a href="/thinking/">All essays →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="thinking-posts">
      {% for essay in collections.essays | reverse | limit(3) %}
      <div class="post">
        <div class="post-tag">{{ essay.data.tag }}</div>
        <div class="post-title"><a href="{{ essay.url }}">{{ essay.data.title }}</a></div>
        <div class="post-date">{{ essay.date | date("MMMM YYYY") }}</div>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
{% endblock %}

{% block footer %}
  <footer class="site-footer">
    <a href="/" class="footer-logo">big<span class="stop">.</span></a>
    <ul class="footer-links">
      <li><a href="/about/">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="/work/">Work</a></li>
      <li><a href="/thinking/">Thinking</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="footer-contact">
      <a href="mailto:al@bigness.uk">al@bigness.uk</a>
    </div>
  </footer>
{% endblock %}
